        <mxCell id="deploy_note" parent="1" style="text;html=1;fontSize=9;fontStyle=0;fillColor=none;strokeColor=none;align=left;verticalAlign=top;fontColor=#545B64;" value="&lt;b&gt;Dev / manual:&lt;/b&gt; &lt;i&gt;deploy-aws&lt;/i&gt; script: package → deploy parent stack. Then &lt;i&gt;npm run build&lt;/i&gt; + &lt;i&gt;s3 sync out/&lt;/i&gt; + invalidation unless you use the pipeline.&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;CodeBuild&lt;/b&gt; assumes the CFN caller role and needs policies for Cognito, DynamoDB, Lambda, API GW (not only CloudFormation API)." vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="52" width="330" x="818" y="338" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>

        <mxCell id="legend_body" parent="1" style="text;html=1;fontSize=8;fontStyle=0;fillColor=#FAFAFA;strokeColor=#D5DBDB;align=left;verticalAlign=top;spacingLeft=6;spacingTop=4;fontColor=#545B64;" value="&lt;b&gt;Runtime:&lt;/b&gt; ① CloudFront serves static app. ② Browser calls &lt;i&gt;NEXT_PUBLIC_API_URL&lt;/i&gt; with Cognito &lt;i&gt;id_token&lt;/i&gt; on &lt;i&gt;/api/*&lt;/i&gt;. ③ Lambda → DynamoDB (metadata) + recordings S3. ④ Admins: &lt;i&gt;cognito:groups&lt;/i&gt;.&#xa;&lt;b&gt;Deploy:&lt;/b&gt; One IaC path per env — CloudFormation today; Terraform planned. Pipeline optional for prod CI." vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="44" width="1048" x="58" y="582" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>

